{"pageProps":{"post":{"title":"반복 선택자 간편하게 쓰기~","date":"2022-09-20","slug":"2022-09-20-css-selector","content":"<h1>🔁 :where(…)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><code>:where(…)</code> 가상 클래스 함수는 <strong>부모 태그는 다른데 자식은 같은 태그</strong>에 공통적인 스타일을 부여할 때 사용한다.</li>\n<li>기존에는 부모 태그 + 중복 자식 태그를 나열하여 작성하는데 <code>:where()</code>가상 선택자를 사용하면 <strong>부모를 한 그룹</strong> 으로 만들어 간단하게 작성할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">// Before</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.header</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.footer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.container</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">red</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">// After</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">:where(</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.header</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.footer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.container</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">red</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h1>🔁 :is(…)</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><code>:is(…)</code> 가상 클래스 함수도 <code>:where(…)</code> 처럼 여러 요소의 스타일 지정 가능</li>\n</ul>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">// Before</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.header</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.footer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.container</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">red</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">// After</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">:is(</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.header</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.footer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.container</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  background: </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">red</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h1>🔁 Example</h1>\n<p class=\"codepen\" data-height=\"300\" data-default-tab=\"html,result\" data-slug-hash=\"KKRadBj\" data-user=\"lprrrr\" style=\"height: 300px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border: 2px solid; margin: 1em 0; padding: 1em;\">\r\n  <span>\r\n    See the Pen <a href=\"https://codepen.io/lprrrr/pen/KKRadBj\">:where() 과 :is()</a> by leepureum (<a href=\"https://codepen.io/lprrrr\">@lprrrr</a>) on <a href=\"https://codepen.io\">CodePen</a>.\r\n  </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<script async src=\"https://cpwebassets.codepen.io/assets/embed/ei.js\"></script>\n<hr>\n<h1>🔁 :where과 :is의 차이</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>설명을 보면 <code>:where</code>과 <code>:is</code>가 같은 의미로 사용이 되는데, 다르게 쓰는 이유는???</p>\n<ul>\n<li>명시도가 다르기 때문에!!!</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"alert\">\r\n  <h6>명시도</h6>\r\n  <p>요소에 적용하는 스타일 반영 순위로 흔히 우리가 아는 적용되는 우선 순위이다.</p>\r\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>where</code>의 명시도는 0 / <code>is</code>는 <code>where</code>보다 높다</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div data-rehype-pretty-code-fragment=\"\"><pre style=\"background-color: #282c34\" tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><code data-language=\"scss\" data-theme=\"default\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">:is(</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.header</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.container</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.footer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  background: salmon; </span><span style=\"color: #7F848E; font-style: italic\">// 해당 스타일이 적용</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">:where(</span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.header</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.container</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">, </span><span style=\"color: #D19A66\">.footer</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">) </span><span style=\"color: #E06C75\">p</span><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\"> {</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">  background: skyblue;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #ABB2BF\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<hr>\n<h1>🔁 지원 범위</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>IE를 제외한 브라우저는 지원 가능</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>:where()</h2>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/blog/posts/css/selector2.png\" alt=\"selector\"></p>\n<h2>:is()</h2>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/blog/posts/css/selector1.png\" alt=\"selector\"></p>"}},"__N_SSG":true}